      • tokenizeArguments

        private static java.util.List<java.lang.String> tokenizeArguments(java.lang.String args)
        Utility method that takes the given arguments, splits them at the whitespaces (space and tab) and turns them into an array of Strings. Other than the StringTokenizer, this method takes care of quotes, such that quoted passages end up being one string.
        参数:
        args - The string to be split.
        返回:
        The array of split strings.
